{"tid":1460631,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"(幫放大)機場入面只有POPO夠膽搞事, 因為無事端就無藉口入我地 大家係機場一定要和理非, 帶頭搞事的肯撚定係鬼","createTime":"2019-08-13T04:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T07:06:48.000Z","uid":81113,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"850db8a37081f948c9e60e6a1002ace2647dfb71","tid":1460631,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:03:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>機場入面只有POPO夠膽搞事, 因為無事端就無藉口入我地<br />\n大家係機場一定要和理非, 帶頭搞事的肯撚定係鬼<br />\n咁樣並唔等於割蓆 , 只係機場交俾和理非, 市區交俾勇武派</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n請認真睇一睇Q&amp;A<br />\n<br />\n我係前狗隊高級督察 狗隊部署你問我答<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460251\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460251</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>去到機場，係要向遊客宣傳，請盡量給予旅客良好印象</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n機場和你飛令成功令深藍變轉汰<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460240</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>就算當故事，都仍然覺得有道理</strong></span>"},{"pid":"fea8e8875311174537d76a85c04b2afabe9bd445","tid":1460631,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:05:57.000Z","msg":"如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"ee7d55a691ba5208f0c287080ccb2280a82ac7cf","tid":1460631,"uid":65738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:06:39.000Z","msg":"即場扯口罩, 記者照妖, 網民起底, 勇武跟進"},{"pid":"3a5eb8f5e1db9620920c73cb7972f60c8f8f86ec","tid":1460631,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"